parameter category: when distribution is uniform, then parameter1 is lower bound, parameter2 is upper bound, parameter3 is step size
when distribution is beta, then parameter1 is alpha, parameter2 is beta
when distribution is gamma, then parameter1 is shape, parameter2 is scale
when distribution is dirichlet, then parameter1 is the first element of alpha, parameter2 is the second element of alpha, parameter3 is the third element, parameter4 is the fourth element
